  "detailed_description": "Barrhell is a short yet challenging game where the player finds themselves stuck in an evil barrel, transformed into a demon at the bottom of a cave system and needs to escape using their newfound form. Jump, and spin the character with precision, launch the barrel by shooting and attaching the tail to objects. Just don't fall along the way! Can you escape and find freedom?<br><br>Flick the mouse to move the barrel!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687680/extras/04052aecc17dbad1231deedc6fab442e.poster.avif?t=1721840427\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687680/extras/04052aecc17dbad1231deedc6fab442e.webm?t=1721840427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Shoot and charge your tail to launch the barrel!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687680/extras/19191400549c110065338798e672dfd9.poster.avif?t=1721840427\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687680/extras/19191400549c110065338798e672dfd9.webm?t=1721840427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Perfectly land on either end of the barrel to stop moving and regain control!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687680/extras/51febb7a55b79ba7f6e1e902a827c329.poster.avif?t=1721840427\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2687680/extras/51febb7a55b79ba7f6e1e902a827c329.webm?t=1721840427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Inspired by Getting Over It with Bennet Foddy.",
